            <p class="chottu-info" style="font-size: 20px;">Acupuncture and acupressure are two techniques commonly used in traditional Chinese medicine to treat nausea and vomiting.</p>

            <h3 style="text-align: left;">Slice a Lemon</h3>
            <p class="chottu-info" style="font-size: 20px;">Citrusy smells, such as those from a freshly sliced lemon, may help reduce nausea in pregnant women.</p>

            <h3 style="text-align: left;">Vitamin B6</h3>
            <p class="chottu-info" style="font-size: 20px;">Vitamin B6 is increasingly recommended as an alternative treatment for pregnant women preferring to avoid anti-nausea medications.

